# - dist/               → TypeScript build output
# - local.settings.json → Local environment variables
# - *.log               → Log files
# - .env*               → Environment files
# - coverage/           → Test coverage reports
# - .cache/             → Various cache directories
```

## Key Directories:
- **`src/functions/`** → Azure Function HTTP triggers (main API endpoints)
- **`src/database/`** → Database clients and migrations
- **`src/models/`** → TypeScript interfaces for data structures
- **`src/services/`** → Business logic and data processing
- **`src/utils/`** → Middleware and helper functions 